{"id":"concepts/climate-change","title":"Climate change","type":"concepts","html":"<blockquote>\n<p>Stub. Earliest dated framing in the corpus: <em>\"the fight of my generation\"</em> (<a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2021-04-19-why-osu\">2021 04 19 why osu</a>). Pre-builder Yahir routed ambition through the climate-impact lens — <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/osu\">OSU</a> chosen partly for <em>\"the influence of nature\"</em> and the <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/sustainability-triple-bottom-line\">triple bottom line</a> business framing. By 2023 the climate framing had been displaced by <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/crypto\">crypto</a> / software ambition vectors — see <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2023-02-10-osig-going-forward\">2023 02 10 osig going forward</a>.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Connections: <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/sustainability-triple-bottom-line\">sustainability triple bottom line</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/osu\">osu</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2021-04-19-why-osu\">2021 04 19 why osu</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"synthesis/from-fitness-to-software-the-brotein-arc\">from fitness to software the brotein arc</a></p>\n","related":[{"id":"concepts/crypto","label":"Crypto"},{"id":"synthesis/from-fitness-to-software-the-brotein-arc","label":"From Fitness To Software The Brotein Arc"},{"id":"summaries/2022-04-13-Geog203_Human-Environment-Geography_Spring-2022","label":"GEOG 203 Syllabus — Spring 2022"},{"id":"entities/osu","label":"Oregon State University (OSU)"},{"id":"summaries/2023-02-10-osig-going-forward","label":"OSIG going forward (the meritocracy reckoning, 2/10/23)"},{"id":"summaries/2021-01-26-Renaissance-Scholarship","label":"Renaissance Scholarship — Brainstorm + Draft Essays"},{"id":"concepts/sustainability-triple-bottom-line","label":"Sustainability Triple Bottom Line"},{"id":"summaries/2021-04-19-why-osu","label":"Why OSU (4/19/21 — sustainability + climate-as-generation-fight)"}]}
